Rating: 3
Prepared this dish with another from the same Bon Appetit issue. Next time, I would either make a half cup less orzo or add another can of chick peas to create a better ratio. Much more lemon juice was needed to enhance the flavor of the dish - added to taste. The oregano and goat cheese were excellent. I would also consider adding roasted red pepper or another color to make the dish more visually appealing. Lastly, make sure you let the orzo cool a bit before adding the goat cheese unless you want it to melt. Wonderful at room temp.